Changing utilities

Overriding excising utilities is possible by using the same key. For example if you want more responsive overflow
utility classes you can do this:

$utilities: (
  "overflow": (
    responsive: true,
    property: overflow,
    values: visible hidden scroll auto,
  ),
);

